{"tid":1305962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好互屌！！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:58:14.000Z","uid":73438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"840be839fc486edf28840633552e971869f0b885","tid":1305962,"uid":73438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"呢排一連串抗爭期間，我同其他frd都會不時覺得「衝還衝都唔係咁鳩衝吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」「咁樣守/圍住有咩意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」但一次又一次，呢啲看似無用嘅行動又有時會有意外收穫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到今次油塘單嘢大家開始互屌，切記：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，各自努力</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家可以討論，可以發表意見，可以講下自己覺得點樣做先好，理據係咩，但要相信前線手足！相信佢哋有智慧、有能力作出最合適嘅判斷，大家揀唔同嘅方法無所謂，之後互相補位提點番就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次單嘢我覺得，和理非有和理非方法做，勇武又有勇武方法做，A餐同B餐，睇大家成本同能力，無話<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定</span></strong>要揀其中一個。勇武話唔可以一味打不還手，要自衛保護自己，我覺得好合理，俾著我喺現場都會打鳩個廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；但呢位義士堅持打不還手，唔係縮沙係企硬，就係要話俾全世界知「抗爭者唔係暴徒班廢中先係暴徒」，呢份情操亦好值得尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。今次呢單嘢同埋連儂牆in general，其實都係宣傳一部份，對象係淺藍淺黃同中間派市民，呢位手足堅持咁做係有佢嘅宣傳效果。<br />\n<br />\n我同意呢啲情況其實係應該自衛，身邊嘅手足亦應該保護被打嘅人，但義士有佢嘅判斷，大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該屌佢on9</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好互屌，繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝 武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2530aa1cdf4a40a099beb2edef859ba89bdbcf8e","tid":1305962,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6bd4bf129e388883cca453648ff214569942aa8","tid":1305962,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=8b75d3f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=4b4d68f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">6.12一周月行動</span> - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10156221199385785%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=ca67a564\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n7.13 - 全民中銀撳錢 - <a href=\"https://t.me/loveBOC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FloveBOC&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d52ea689\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/loveBOC</a><br />\n7.13 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">光復上水</span> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=2b10f022\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32eEvRm</a><br />\n7.14 - <span style=\"color: gold;\">沙田區大遊行</span><span style=\"color: red;\">(死線)</span> - <a href=\"http://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li